{"tid":260069,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"哈利卡尼獲球迷選為最佳球員","createTime":"2017-05-27T12:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-27T14:16:41.000Z","uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23c7b628542d8041a336d4991182dba74e835787","tid":260069,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:19:00.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=JztM1fgw8aysWUEKtbiZ6uargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=f7f4e04f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】熱刺射手哈利卡尼獲球迷選為本賽季英超最佳球員，確倒車路士的尼高路簡迪及夏薩特。<br />\n在這個由天空體育網站及apps進行的選舉，得到本季英超神射手殊榮的熱刺前鋒哈利卡尼（Harry Kane），在逾<span style=\"color: red;\">49000</span>個投票中得到16378票，比第2名得13515票的車路士中場尼高路簡迪多出近3000票。後者在本季3大獎項，即英格蘭球員員先生、足球先生及英超最佳球員都力壓群雄。排第3的夏薩特已被兩人遠遠拋離，得票為8412票；至於第4至第6位依次為阿仙奴鋒將阿歷斯山齊士（6727票）、熱刺中場迪利阿里（3507票）及愛華頓前鋒盧卡古（955票）。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3e2456b9bf3396f2673952f2e0ec5492de8fd6","tid":260069,"uid":36138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T12:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />木土派"},{"pid":"241f99a6d8183b25f0ea867ea1e2919865e78bfb","tid":260069,"uid":16870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T14:16:41.000Z","msg":"本土萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}